%3E%2C%20lower%20cholesterol%2C%20and%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20colon%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpepsico-ceo-says-fiber-will-be-the-next-protein-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPepsiCo's%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ramon%20Laguarta%20did%20beat%20Kempczinski%20to%20the%20punch%2C%20predicting%20in%20an%20October%20earnings%20call%20that%20%26quot%3Bfiber%20will%20be%20the%20next%20protein.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f35fe67-f69d-4dfc-800e-d9e758cded55%5C%22%3ESweet%20and%20spicy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20item%20on%20his%20list%20was%20a%20unique%20flavor%20combination%3A%20%26quot%3BSweet%20and%20spicy%20together%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20big%20food%20trend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFast%20food%20chains%20have%20already%20jumped%20on%20the%20trend.%20In%202025%2C%20chains%20like%20Chipotle%2C%20KFC%2C%20and%20Taco%20Bell%20all%20rolled%20out%20hot%20honey%20dipping%20sauces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20trend%20is%20a%20continuation%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Bsauces%26quot%3B%20prediction%20from%20last%20year.%20In%202025%2C%20Kempczinski%20said%20sauces%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20main%20dish%2C%20would%20be%20diners'%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpicy%20is%20always%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20then.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20you%20might%20see%20some%20honey%20or%20some%20sweet%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20does%20have%20a%20sweet-spicy%20sauce%20offering%20in%20its%20Creamy%20Chili%20McCrispy%20Strip%20Dip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b22fd3fe-fe53-40db-8f16-2524ae9a640a%5C%22%3EInteresting%20drinks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20lastly%2C%20Kempczinski%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20beverage%20innovation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20year%2C%20fast%20food%20chains%20have%20rolled%20out%20new%20beverages%2C%20with%20some%2C%20such%20as%20Taco%20Bell%20and%20Chick-fil-A%2C%20launching%20new%20beverage-focused%2