ty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20significant%20backlash%2C%20Grok%20won't%20generate%20AI%20images%20of%20real%20people%20in%20sexualized%20clothing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECalifornia%20Attorney%20General%20Rob%20Bonta%20said%20he%20launched%20an%20investigation%20into%20Grok's%20AI%20deepfakes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIndonesia%20and%20Malaysia%20suspended%20Grok%20amid%20concerns%20over%20sexualized%20images%20of%20women%20and%20minors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGrok%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20allowed%20to%20create%20AI%20photos%20of%20real%20people%20in%20sexualized%20or%20revealing%20clothing%2C%20after%20widespread%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-limits-grok-ai-image-tool-sexualized-deepfake-backlash-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eglobal%20backlash%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20implemented%20technological%20measures%20to%20prevent%20the%20Grok%20account%20from%20allowing%20the%20editing%20of%20images%20of%20real%20people%20in%20revealing%20clothing%20such%20as%20bikinis%2C%26quot%3B%20X's%20safety%20account%20said%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20on%20the%20platform%20on%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BThis%20restriction%20applies%20to%20all%20users%2C%20including%20paid%20subscribers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20was%20announced%20hours%20after%20California's%20top%20prosecutor%2C%20Rob%20Bonta%2C%20said%20he%20launched%20an%20investigation%20into%20sexualized%20AI%20deepfakes%2C%20including%20those%20of%20children%2C%20generated%20by%20Grok.%20Bonta%20said%20that%20there%20had%20been%20a%20flood%20of%20reports%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20that%20Grok%20users%20were%20taking%20pictures%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-grok-remove-clothes-ai-images-women-minors-backlash-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewomen%20and%20minors%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20found%20online%20and%20using%20the%20AI%20model%20to%20undress%20them%20in%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BxAI%20can%20and%20should%20put%20better%20safeguards%20in%20place%20to%20protect%20children%20and%20women%20from%20the%20harms%20of%20sexually%20explicit%20materials%20being%20generated%20without%20their%20consent%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20California%20Attorney%20General's%20office%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20Grok's%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20is%20an%20encouraging%20development%2C%20California%20DOJ%20is%20investigating%20to%20determine%20whether%20xAI%20violated%20the%20law%20with%20the%20conduct%20that%20has%20occurred.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndonesia%20and%20Malaysia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findonesia-bans-grok-generating-sexual-deepfakes-women-children-ai-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esuspended%20Grok%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20of%20the%20images%2C%20the%20first%20countries%20in%20the%20world%20to%20ban%20the%20AI%20tool.%20Lawmakers%20in%20the%20UK%20publicly%20considered%20a%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Wednesday's%20blog%20post%2C%20the%20social%20media%20company%20reiterated%20that%20image%20creation%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20edit%20images%20via%20Grok%20on%20the%20X%20platform%20will%20now%20only%20be%20available%20to%20paid%20users%20as%20an%20additional%20safety%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20restricted%20non-paying%20users%20last%20week%20after%20complaints%20from%20officials%20globally%2C%20but%20it%20was%20slammed%20for%20being%20insufficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bsimply%20turns%20an%20AI%20feature%20that%20allows%20the%20creation%20of%20unlawful%20images%20into%20a%20premium%20service.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20who%20owns%20xAI%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-all-hands-agi-superintelligence-funding-success-optimus-space%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaker%20of%20Grok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20the%20UK%20government%20wanted%20%26quot%3Bany%20excuse%20for%20censorship%26quot%3B%20in%20response%20to%20a%20post%20questioning%20why%20AI%20tools%20like%20Gemini%20and%20ChatGPT%20were%20not%20being%20looked%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20few%20hours%20before%20X's%20official%20account%20posted%20about%20the%20ban%20on%20creating%20sexualized%20images%2C%20Musk%20asked%20users%20to%20try%20to%20get%20around%20the%20AI%20model's%20image%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarmer's%20office%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrok-stops-users-making-sexualized-ai-images-backlash-xai-musk-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1768439853000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69683d7504eda4732f2f1ba6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrok-stops-users-making-sexualized-ai-images-backlash-xai-musk-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Grok%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20allowed%20to%20edit%20photos%20of%20real%20people%20to%20show%20them%20in%20sexualized%20or%20revealing%20clothing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrok-stops-users-making-sexualized-ai-images-backlash-xai-musk-2026-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bruno%20Mars%20Adds%2030%2B%20New%20Dates%20to%20%E2%80%98The%20Romantic%20Tour%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1768439510000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236631834%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bruno%20Mars%20has%20added%2030