0choice%20for%20itty-bitty%20kittens%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20drawback%20of%20this%20box%20is%20that%20the%20low%20entry%20limits%20the%20litter%20depth.%20Some%20cats%20prefer%20digging%20in%20a%20few%20inches%2C%20but%20the%20fill%20line%20on%20this%20box%20sits%20at%20about%20an%20inch.%20I%20filled%20it%20just%20slightly%20above%20the%20line%2C%20and%20while%20litter%20reached%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20entry%20after%20my%20cats%20used%20it%2C%20none%20actually%20tumbled%20out.%20An%20aggressive%20digger%2C%20however%2C%20will%20likely%20cause%20some%20litter%20to%20spill%20from%20the%20entryway.%20Shallow%20litter%20depth%20also%20means%20less%20clean%20litter%20is%20available%20for%20your%20cat%20after%20they%20eliminate%2C%20so%20you%20should%20scoop%20the%20box%20more%20frequently.%20To%20help%20manage%20litter%20scatter%2C%20I%20recommend%20pairing%20the%20box%20with%20a%20litter%20mat%2C%20such%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15116968408k7i-20%26h%3De0a122bbe3dcde1d4c3ba61e0ec0ba446ba134476fde7f0c78826ee604fc83f2%26postID%3D6967cd0f8fd5028cf2cf54aa%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-cat-litter-boxes%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB01MDNDDYS%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGorilla%20Grip%20Cat%20Litter%20Trapping%20Mat%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d227fdc2-5a9c-416a-ac8a-72a7d516130b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20stainless%20steel%5C%22%3EBest%20stainless%20steel%20litter%20box%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20durable%20stainless%20steel%20Frisco%20litter%20box%20offers%20a%20significant%20advantage%20over%20traditional%20plastic%20litter%20boxes%3A%20It%20resists%20the%20scratches%20that%20plastic%20boxes%20accumulate%20over%20time.%20Those%20scratches%20can%20harbor%20bacteria%20and%20unpleasant%20odors%2C%20even%20when%20the%20box%20is%20cleaned%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%