%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20some%20cats%20don't%20mind%20a%20covered%20box%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20it's%20large%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20comfortable.%20That's%20why%20I%20chose%20the%20Frisco%20Extra-Large%20Hooded%20Cat%20Litter%20Box%20as%20the%20best%20covered%20litter%20box%20option.%20It%20has%20a%20larger%20interior%20compared%20to%20other%20covered%20boxes%20and%20a%20removable%20cover%2C%20giving%20you%20the%20flexibility%20to%20adjust%20the%20setup%20if%20your%20cat%20is%20hesitant.%20With%20the%20cover%20in%20place%2C%20a%20built-in%20charcoal%20filter%20provides%20extra%20odor%20control%20between%20cleanings.%20Even%20without%20the%20cover%2C%20the%20high%20sides%20help%20contain%20messes%2C%20which%20is%20especially%20useful%20for%20cats%20who%20tend%20to%20%26quot%3Belevator%20pee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20box%20has%20a%20semi-opaque%20plastic%20door%20to%20help%20prevent%20odors%20from%20escaping.%20As%20you%20might%20guess%2C%20that%20just%20traps%20smells%20inside%20with%20your%20cat%20and%20can%20make%20the%20space%20feel%20even%20more%20confining.%20For%20these%20reasons%2C%20it's%20best%20to%20remove%20the%20door%2C%20which%20easily%20snaps%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232ac8dfa-c12e-4dff-81d8-e8e32a6c163c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20DIY%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20DIY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20creating%20a%20DIY%20litter%20box%2C%20a%20wide%2C%20flat%20plastic%20storage%20container%20is%20an%20ideal%20and%20cost-effective%20stand-in%20for%20a%20traditional%20box.%20In%20fact%2C%20Quagliozzi%20and%20Sung%20often%20recommend%20their%20clients%20consider%20this%20DIY%20version%20since%20many%20traditional%20litter%20boxes%20are%20too%20small%20for%20more%20than%20one%20cat%20to%20use%20several%20times%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sterilite%2041-Quart%20Storage%20Box%20is%20made%20from%20durable%2C%20clear%20plastic.%20Its%20interior%20dimensions%20of%2029%203%2F8%20inches%20by%2018%20inches%20provide%20a%20cat%20with%20plenty%20of%20room%20to%20perform%20natural%20behaviors%20like%20digging%20and%20covering%20their%20waste.%20A%20box%20this%20big%20is%20especially%20important%20for%20extra-large%20breeds%20such%20as%20the%20Maine%20Coon%2C%20the%20biggest%20domestic%20cat%2C%20which%20can%20reach%20up%20to%20an%20astonishing%2040%20inches%20in%20length.%20Because%20the%20box%20is%20waterproof%2C%20it%20won't%20leak%20any%20excess%20urine%20that%20goes%20uncaptured%20by%20the%20litter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%206-inch-high%20sides%2C%20the%20box%20is%20shallow%20enough%20for%20most%20cats%20to%20enter%20and%20exit%20easily%2C%20but%20you%20can%20also%20cut%20a%20low%20front%20entry.%20Use%20a%20pair%20of%20wire%20cutters%20to%20cut%20the%20entrance%20to%20your%20desired%20height%20and%20width%2C%20then%20tap%20over%20the%20edges%20with%20duct%20tape.%20People%20with%20cats%20that%20aggressively%20scratch%20and%20kick%20their%20litter%20may%20need%20to%20do%20more%20floor%20cleanup%20than%20they%20would%20with%20a%20litter%20pan%20with%20higher%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b893a33b-f63b-4c96-9e19-294421821fe3%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20top-entry%5C%22%3EBest%20top-entry%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESung%20and%20Quagliozzi%20say%20cats%20need%20choices%20to%20feel%20secure%2C%20which%20includes%20having%20at%20least%20two%20litter%20box%20areas%20per%20cat%20in%20your%20home.%20Having%20more%20than%20one%20way%20in%20and%20out%20of%20a%20box%20can%20also%20make%20a%20big%20difference.%20While%20an%20uncovered%20box%20with%20unlimited%20exit%20routes%20is%20best%2C%20a%20covered%20box%20with%20both%20a%20top%20and%20side%20entrance%20gives%20your%20cat%20more%20control%20over%20how%20they%20come%20and%20go.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20Modkat's%20XL%20Litter%20Box%20is%20our%20top%20recommendation%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-top-entry-litter-box%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blan