ng%20a%20lawyer%20with%20close%20ties%20to%20Adams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdams%20told%20journalists%20Monday%20morning%20that%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyc-token-crash-eric-adams-crypto-meme-coin-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENYC%20Token%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20project%20would%20generate%20money%20to%20fund%20blockchain%20education%20for%20underserved%20New%20Yorkers%20and%20fight%20antisemitism%20and%20%26quot%3Banti-Americanism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20didn't%20say%20how%2C%20or%20specify%20who%20he%20was%20working%20with%2C%20but%20said%20he%20wasn't%20drawing%20a%20salary%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project's%20website%20mentions%20an%20entity%20called%20C18%20Digital%20LLC%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbuynyctoken.com%2Fterms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20terms%20of%20service%3C%2Fa%3E.%20An%20entity%20with%20that%20name%20was%20formed%20in%20Delaware%20on%20December%2030.%20The%20certificate%20of%20formation%20was%20signed%20by%20Sefi%20Zvieli.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20City%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20news%20outlet%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecity.nyc%2F2023%2F04%2F13%2Ffrank-carone-yosef-zvieli-brooklyn-shelter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20in%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Zvieli%20avoided%20foreclosure%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bfilthy%2C%20fetid%2C%20and%20dangerous%26quot%3B%20block%20of%20student%20housing%20he%20owned%20in%20Brooklyn%20by%20inking%20a%20deal%20to%20rent%20it%20to%20a%20New%20York%20City-financed%20nonprofit%20as%20a%20homeless%20shelter%20for%20%243.5%20million%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20said%20he%20snagged%20the%20deal%20after%20hiring%20Frank%20Carone%2C%20a%20lawyer%20with%20close%20ties%20to%20Adams%2C%20after%20Adams%20had%20won%20the%20New%20York%20City%20mayoral%20election%20but%20before%20he%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20mayor.%20Zvieli%20has%20also%20been%20listed%20in%20public%20records%20for%20various%20New%20York%20companies%20and%20has%20been%20described%20by%20Israeli%20news%20outlets%20as%20a%20hotel%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20what%20role%20Zvieli%20played%20in%20NYC%20Token%20beyond%20signing%20the%20formation%20papers.%20He%20didn't%20reply%20to%20an%20email%20address%20listed%20for%20him%20in%20website%20registration%20records.%20Carone%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20token's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjup.ag%2Ftokens%2FHo5fkxk9uqUuVN5kt7TUFacduWCpKPAuYkM9HD3KAXA2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrading%20history%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20hours%20after%20Adams%20plugged%20it%3A%20After%20peaking%20around%2050%20cents%20per%20token%2C%20its%20price%20fell%20to%20less%20than%209%20cents%20per%20token.%20It%20has%20since%20risen%20to%20around%2013%20cents%20per%20token.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20users%20who%20said%20they%20had%20purchased%20the%20coin%20expressed%20outrage%2C%20accusing%20Adams%20or%20people%20affiliated%20with%20the%20project%20of%20stealing%20funds.%20The%20crypto%20analytics%20company%20Bubblemaps%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fbubblemaps%2Fstatus%2F2010890093431832789%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20posts%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20wallet%20withdrew%20%242.5%20million%20of%20sales%20proceeds%20from%20a%20liquidity%20pool%20associated%20with%20NYC%20Token%20shortly%20before%20its%20value%20collapsed%2C%20before%20putting%20about%20%241.5%20million%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElissa%20Buchter%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20NYC%20Token%2C%20said%20in%20an%20email%20that%20the%20token's%20backers%20were%20not%20responsible%20for%20its%20wild%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20market%20maker%20made%20adjustments%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20keep%20trading%20running%20smoothly%2C%20and%20as%20part%20of%20this%20process%2C%20moved%20liquidity%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20an%20email.%20%26quot%3BThe%20team%